variable defined: HEAR=You hear wind.

Approach going West.

script
put pit in cavern 3
put player in cavern 5
enter command w
check message You hear wind. was printed true
enter command e
check message You hear wind. was printed false
 
  ''Approach going North.''
put player in cavern 9
enter command n
check message You hear wind. was printed true
enter command s
check message You hear wind. was printed false
 
  ''Approach going East.''
put player in cavern 1
enter command e
check message You hear wind. was printed true
enter command w
check message You hear wind. was printed false

put player in cavern 6
enter command s
